’Щ@c87577e5fdbd9a61c47f49b7646dd909986418e88a6d495f52bf939c76d48185ЪATitle: title: bits rol
Path: Examples
Content:
Rotate left a number with 2 bits
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 17 | bits rol 2
68

```
Rotate left a list of numbers with 2 bits
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [5 3 2] | bits rol 2
в•­в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”¬в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв•®
в”‚ 0 в”‚ 20 в”‚
в”‚ 1 в”‚ 12 в”‚
в”‚ 2 в”‚  8 в”‚
в•°в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”ґв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв•Ї


```
rotate left binary data
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 0x[c0 ff ee] | bits rol 10
Length: 3 (0x3) bytes | null_char printable whitespace ascii_other non_ascii
00000000:   ff bb 03                                             Г—Г—вЂў


```
